Architecture: amd64
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: retroarch | libretro-frontend, ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Libretro wrapper for the Beetle SATURN core
 This wrapper makes Beetle SATURN core API compatible with libretro, thus
 allowing its use with libretro frontends, such as RetroArch.
 .
 Beetle is a fork of Mednafen for libretro. This core emulates the Sega Saturn
 console.
 .
 Sega Saturn is a registered trademark of Sega Games Co., Ltd. Mednafen/Beetle
 SATURN is not affiliated with or endorsed by any of the companies mentioned.
 The emulator is for educational and development purposes only and it may not
 be used to play games you do not legally own.
